; テオの回想～町からの脱出



;■プロローグ２・ブルーとの出会い

;◇イベント01・テオの回想
*past_1

; 町中

; 回想を見たという記録を付ける
@eval exp='f.readPastEpisode = true'

@wait time=1000
@mu f=worry
[texton w=0]
[？？？]「Yes, good job.」[k]
@se f=coin
@eval exp='game.party.gold -= 20000'
[テオ f=05]「Ah...」[k]
The moment I and Max left the bar, someone snatched the bag of gold coins from my hand.[k]
[textoff]
@fg c=ブルー e=帯刀 f=02
[texton w=1]
[ブルー f=02]「Yo.」[k]
[マックス f=12]「Oh, Blue...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Blue...」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「You're late. I was tired of waiting.」[k]
The person who took the bag of gold coins was an adventurer named Blue.[k]
Blue took our reward as if he was the one who'd earned it, opened the bag, and stuck his hand inside.[k]
[ブルー f=02]「Here, your share.」[k]
@se f=coinsingle
@eval exp='game.party.gold += 30'
He took a few gold coins from his gold coin bag and handed them to me and Max.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Max and I accepted it without saying a word.[k]
[ブルー f=02]「See you.」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
[texton]
After saying this, Blue disappeared to the back of the bar with the bag of gold coins.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[マックス f=19]「...Damn, that's all we got. Screw him. We're the ones who worked for it.」[k]
Max whispered.[k]
Yes, it was definitely me and Max who accomplished this quest.[k]
But... Blue reaped the rewards, as normal.[k]
But we can't complain about him.[k]
That was simply the relationship we had with Blue.[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
@w1

; ここから１年前の回想
[texton]
1 year ago [―――][k]
As a new adventurer, I was full of hope for the life of adventure that was about to begin.[k]
[textoff]
@w1

*_past_1_from_demo
@saveon
@mu f=town
@bg f=0007
[texton w=1]
[テオ e=布の服 f=02]「There we go.」[k]
After moving my belongings into my new home and some light cleaning, I took a break and was excited about the adventurous life I was about to embark on.[k]
This is a room in an apartment. This is my base of operations in Bravetown, a town where adventurers gather.[k]
From now on, I will be staying here and working as an adventurer.[k]
This apartment is actually a bit nicer than many others here. It has larger rooms and is close to the guild and the tavern.[k]
One of my father's acquaintances arranged this when I made my debut as an adventurer.[k]
It was all thanks to the prestige of my late father.[k]
Dad was a very famous adventurer, and his special abilities as a demon hunter made him famous throughout the world.[k]
Unfortunately, he passed away at a young age. Still, I wanted to become an adventurer like him, and came to this town as the first step. My mother in my hometown is also supporting me.[k]
So, let's do it! For my dad in heaven, I'll definitely become an adventurer like him![k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Well, where should we go first?[k]
...After all, being an adventurer is all about forming a party and doing quests to make a name for yourself, right?[k]
Okay, let's visit the guild and the tavern first![k]
[textoff]
@out

; ブルーとの出会い
@bg f=0012
@mu f=bar
[texton]
I went to the bar.[k]
[テオ f=01]「Wow... There are so many people here...」[k]
The tavern also served as a hub for quests, and was crowded with many adventurers during the day.[k]
For now, let's go to the guild and register as an adventurer. If you don't register, you won't be able to form a party, and you won't be introduced to jobs.[k]
[テオ f=02]「Okay, I'll get to this later, but first I need to get to the guild...」[k]
@se f=beat
@quake time=500
@flash
∗thump!∗[k]
[テオ f=11]「Ah!」[k]
That's when I bumped into someone.[k]
[textoff]
@fg c=ブルー e=帯刀 f=06
@wait time=500
[texton]
[ブルー f=06]「...」[k]
Behind me stood a large adventurer.[k]
[テオ f=12]「Sorry! I was a bit distracted...」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「...」[k]
@fg c=ブルー f=02
[ブルー f=02]「...Don't worry. You don't look familiar. You new here?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Ah, yes.」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「Well... Where do you live?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「I live in an apartment right next to this bar.」[k]
@fg r=エリック e=通常 f=02
[エリック f=01]「Wow, so it's right around the corner.」[k]
Another adventurer behind him muttered.[k]
[テオ f=12]「Y-yes...」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「I'm Blue. This is Eric.」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「There's probably many things you don't understand since you just got here. If you have any problems, you can count on us.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Y-yes! Thank you very much!」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「See you next time.」[k]
[エリック f=02]「... ∗grin∗」[k]
@cl
[テオ f=02]「...」[k]
Phew, it's nice to meet a kind senior.[k]
At first I thought he looked a little scary, but he seems dependable. This is a good start.[k]
Okay, keep it up and look for a job with a party first![k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05

; マックスとの出会い
@bg f=0013
@mu f=guild
[texton]
Next I went to the guild.[k]
In the room, several young adventurers were going through the formalities.[k]
@fg c=マックス e=革鎧,布のズボン f=01
[マックス f=01]「Hey, you, are you new here?」[k]
This time I was approached by a man who appeared to be an elf.[k]
[テオ f=02]「Uh-uh.」[k]
[マックス f=03]「Actually, I'm in the same boat! I was wondering if you'd like to join my party? I just got here and I'm a little nervous!」[k]
What a surprise, an offer to form a party out of the blue. I'm very grateful.[k]
[テオ f=01]「Yes! Thank you very much! My name is [テオ], I look forward to working with you.」[k]
[マックス f=03]「I'm Max! Nice to meet you, [テオ]!」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05

@bg f=0016
[texton]
[マックス f=09]「It's hard finding work for us newbies...」[k]
[テオ f=02]「It can't be helped. I'll come back tomorrow to look for another job.」[k]
After hitting it off and forming a party, Max and I went to the bar to look for work.[k]
However, we could not find a suitable job today, so Max and I decided to return to our lodgings.[k]
[マックス f=01]「By the way, you have a nice looking sword～!」[k]
[テオ f=02]「It's a memento of my father, who was an adventurer.」[k]
[マックス f=01]「I see. Your father must have been a great adventurer to have such a fine sword.」[k]
Max looks at my sword with envy.[k]
[テオ f=02]「Well, this is where I live.」[k]
[マックス f=12]「What?! That's a great place! I'm at the inn at the end of the street, three doors down.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Come visit me if you want. You're welcome to.」[k]
[マックス f=03]「I'll definitely stop by. See you tomorrow!」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05

; テオの家
; ブルーたちによる歓迎会
@bg f=0008
@mu f=inn
[texton]
[テオ f=02]「Okay, that's good for the first day.」[k]
I'm glad I found a teammate on day one. Max seems friendly and personable and we seem to get along well.[k]
I got to know some seniors who seemed dependable, so I have nothing to complain about.[k]
@se f=knock
∗knock knock∗[k]
[テオ f=06]「Hmm?」[k]
I heard a knock on my door.[k]
I've only been living here one day, and I don't know anyone in town yet. So I wonder if it's Max.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Yes, who is it?」[k]
@se f=door2
@fg l=ブルー b
@fg r=エリック f=02
[ブルー f=02]「Yo, rookie!」[k]
[エリック f=02]「...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Aaa...」[k]
To my surprise, it was the senior adventurers I had just met at the bar.[k]
Why are they here? I didn't tell them about this house...[k]
[ブルー f=02]「I just happened to see you enter this house, so I decided to pay you a visit.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Ah... I see...」[k]
Well, this house is just around the corner from the bar, I suppose.[k]
[ブルー f=05]「What is it? Am I bothering you?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Oh, no, not at all...」[k]
I smile and desperately deny it.[k]
...This man is a seasoned adventurer. I mustn't do anything to offend him...[k]
[テオ f=12]「Oh, um... You were Mr. Blue and Mr. Eric?」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「Blue's fine.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Eh?」[k]
[ブルー f=01]「We're friends now, right? Let's not be strangers.」[k]
[テオ f=13]「Uh... Uh, yeah. Thank you, Blue... Nice to meet you.」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「Yeah. Nice to meet you.」[k]
[エリック f=05]「...By the way, rookie.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Ah, yes, what is it?」[k]
[エリック f=05]「How long are you going to keep us standing on your doorstep?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「I'm so sorry! Please, come in.」[k]
@cl
I hastily let them in.[k]
[テオ f=12]「I'm sorry, I didn't realize...」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「What, don't worry about it... Hmm.」[k]
Blue and Eric went up to the room and began to wander around the room, looking around.[k]
[テオ f=12]「What is it?」[k]
@fg l=ブルー b
@fg r=エリック
[ブルー f=02]「...Wow, you live in a nice place, you know that?」[k]
[エリック f=01]「I'm jealous of your spacious room. When I was a rookie, I could only live in a small, shabby room.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
Apparently, in their eyes, my temporary housing is pretty good.[k]
This place was introduced to me by an adventurer who was an acquaintance of my father.[k]
My father, Siegwart, who was famous as a demon hunter, made many acquaintances during his lifetime.[k]
In this town where adventurers gather, there is a real estate agency manager whom my father had gotten to know very well, and he found me this room.[k]
Being the son of adventurer Siegwart, I might have been given a slightly better place.[k]
[ブルー f=02]「Well, let's get started.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「Oh, what?」[k]
[ブルー f=01]「It's obvious. Your welcome party.」[k]
Blue then shows a large bottle of sake that he brought with him.[k]
[テオ f=10]「Oh, really? Now?」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「Huh? What's wrong with you?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「H-huh...?」[k]
Oh no. I was going to clean up my room now...[k]
[エリック f=05]「Hey, you. You're not going to turn down Blue's offer, are you?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「No, no! I never meant to...」[k]
[ブルー f=01]「Then it's settled. All right, let's have a toast to the start of [テオ]'s life as an adventurer!」[k]
[テオ f=13]「Y-yes, thank you.」[k]
...Oh well. I'll clean up after they leave.[k]
My seniors are going to celebrate with me. It wouldn't feel right to refuse.[k]
I accepted it and decided to join them for a drink.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@wait time=1000
@bg f=0008
@mu f=trick
[texton]
[―――]A few hours later.[k]
[ブルー f=01]「Here, [テオ]. You drink more, too.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Sorry, I'm not much of a drinker...」[k]
[エリック f=05]「What's the matter with you? Blue is offering, and you're going to turn him down?」[k]
[テオ f=13]「No, I would never... I'm sorry! I'll take it after all!」[k]
[ブルー f=01]「Oh, that's all right. Here, drink more.」[k]
[エリック f=05]「You're a bit flippant. Don't say things that offend people when they're having fun!」[k]
[テオ f=13]「Sorry, I'll take care...」[k]
[ブルー f=01]「Okay, I'll have a drink too!」[k]
∗glug!∗ ∗glug!∗[k]
[エリック f=01]「Yo! That's Blue! Great drinking!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
In the end, the party continued until dawn...[k]
[textoff]
@out
@wait time=1000

; 翌朝・テオの家
@bg f=0015
@mu f=town
[texton]
The next day -[k]
@fg c=マックス
[マックス f=03]「Yo! [テオ]!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Ah... Max...」[k]
When I got ready and went outside, I ran into Max just in front of the door.[k]
[マックス f=01]「I came to get you. Let's find a good job today!」[k]
[マックス f=06]「...Hmm? What's the matter, [テオ], you look kind of pale?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「No, actually I was drinking till morning yesterday...」[k]
I told Max what had happened last night.[k]
[マックス f=03]「Ha～ That was tough. But you're lucky to have an influential senior like you.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「That's true, but...」[k]
[マックス f=01]「Anyway [テオ], let's go to the bar right now and look for a job.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Yeah, okay.」[k]
If you don't accept jobs and do the work, you are not an adventurer.[k]
Take a request at the bar at any cost and take your first step as an adventurer![k]
[textoff]
@out
@w1

; 酒場の受付
@bg f=0012
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「...」[k]
[マックス f=09]「...I can't believe they're out of jobs.」[k]
We visited the quest desk at the bar. To our surprise, today's work was already gone.[k]
The receptionist said that if you don't come early in the morning, you may lose out. I guess I was taking it too easy.[k]
[マックス f=05]「This isn't a good start～!」[k]
[テオ f=02]「It can't be helped. I'll come back earlier tomorrow.」[k]
[マックス f=01]「I guess so. Well, I'm free today, but what am I going to do now～?」[k]
@fg r=エリック b
@fg c=ブルー e=帯刀
[ブルー f=02]「Hey, good to see you again.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Aaa...」[k]
Suddenly, Blue showed up with Eric in tow.[k]
[エリック f=01]「What are you guys doing here?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Oh, actually...」[k]
I told them that I couldn't get a job.[k]
[ブルー f=01]「Hahahaha, that's a mistake I make a lot at first.」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「But rejoice. I'll let you guys help me out.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Eh?」[k]
[マックス f=05]「Work? Yours?」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「Yes, I'll let you come with us. You can experience what adventure is like as a member of my party.」[k]
[マックス f=11]「Are you serious?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Are you sure? We just met you...」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「It would be a shame to come all this way to take on your first job and not be allowed to do anything. So as a special treat, I'll take you along.」[k]
[テオ f=13]「Oh, thank you very much, Blue!」[k]
[マックス f=03]「We are very happy to have met you! Thank you so much!」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「That's all right. Well, now that we've decided that, let's get going.」[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
@w1

; ブルーの冒険に同行
; ダンジョン内
@bg f=0061 b
@mu f=evil
@blood
@fgf c=ブルー e=帯刀
[texton]
∗shaaaaaah!∗[k]
[name n=Monster]「Gwaaaah!」[k]
[マックス f=11]「Amazing...! 」[k]
In the first dungeon the four of us visited together, Blue struck down the first monster that appeared with a single blow.[k]
With inhuman power and quick movements that did not match his large physique, he slew middle-ranking monsters one after another.[k]
He easily defeated monsters that would be impossible for me... This is the difference in level, isn't it?[k]
[ブルー f=02]「Phew, that took care of it.」[k]
[マックス f=03]「Blue, that's great! You took them down in no time at all!」[k]
[エリック f=01]「This is nothing for Blue, ya know?」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「Yeah, well...」[k]
[テオ f=12]「...」[k]
This is truly amazing. This is the skill of a veteran adventurer.[k]
...I wonder if the day will ever come when I reach this level.[k]
[エリック f=01]「Well, we've killed most of the monsters we've been asked to take down, so let's head back, Blue.」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w1

; ダンジョンから帰還中
@bg f=0015
@mu f=guild
[texton]
[マックス f=03]「Wow～! That fight earlier was really awesome! As expected of Blue!」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「Hmph, it's not that big of a deal.」[k]
[マックス f=03]「Hey, [テオ]! I'm really glad to have met Blue!」[k]
[テオ f=14]「Y-yeah...」[k]
[マックス f=03]「By the way, Blue! The reward for today's quest was 10,000G, right? How much will you share with us?」[k]
[ブルー f=08]「Huh?!」[k]
Suddenly, Blue's eyes instantly turned angry![k]
[マックス f=13]「Ah, well, my share of today's reward...」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「There's no such thing.」[k]
[マックス f=12]「What?」[k]
[エリック f=08]「You newbies don't get a share of the profits, do you? Don't get carried away.」[k]
[マックス f=12]「Huh... but...」[k]
[エリック f=08]「Besides, most of today's quests were accomplished thanks to Blue. Why should we share with you guys?」[k]
[マックス f=12]「Ah...」[k]
[マックス f=13]「...Yes, that's right! I was just asking! I'm sorry!」[k]
[マックス f=10]（What the heck? We were the ones killing the other weaklings, and carrying their stuff too...）[k]
[テオ f=02]（Oh well. It was a good experience.）[k]
Max is disgruntled. Well, he says his wallet is strained already, so he must be desperate when it comes to money.[k]
But I have to admit what Eric said earlier. Certainly today's quest could not have been accomplished without Blue.[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
I was more shocked by the overwhelming difference in power as an adventurer than by the fact that I was forced to work for free.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@wait time=1000

; 自宅・翌朝
@bg f=0007
@mu f=town
@fg c=マックス f=03
[texton]
The next morning. Max came to my house before dawn.[k]
Max is in high spirits. We were late yesterday and couldn't get a quest, so he decided to go to the bar early today.[k]
[マックス f=03]「Come on, let's get to the bar! [テオ]!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「I know. Don't be in such a hurry.」[k]
[textoff]
@out
