; 酒場の受付
@bg f=0012
[texton]
[受付]「Good morning, you are the first to arrive!」[k]
When I visited the reception desk at the bar, to my surprise, no one had arrived yet.[k]
[マックス f=13]「Ahahaha... Was it too early?」[k]
[受付]「It's wonderful that you're so motivated. I'll find a special job for you.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Really?! Thank you very much!」[k]
[textoff]
@out t=0
@w05
[texton]
Just as the receptionist said, it was a nice job. The pay wasn't bad, and the difficulty level was just right.[k]
Despite all the difficulties, Max and I managed to complete the request.[k]
[textoff]
@out t=0
@w1

; 自宅での酒盛り
@bg f=0007
[texton]
Evening. We had successfully completed our first quest and received a reward from the client. I invited Max to my house and we were celebrating.[k]
[マックス f=03]「Wow, you're good at magic and swords, you know? Thanks to you, we were able to finish the quest easily!」[k]
[テオ f=02]「The quest went well, thanks to your thief skills.」[k]
[マックス f=03]「I think we make a great team! Let's do it again! Well, tonight, for the first time in ages, I'm going to indulge myself with the rewards of today's quest...」[k]
@se f=knock
∗knock knock∗[k]
[マックス f=01]「Hmm? Someone's here?」[k]
[テオ f=06]「I'll be out in a minute.」[k]
@se f=door2
I open the door to my room...[k]
@mu f=trick
@fg c=9017 left=200 top=200 b
@fg r=エリック b
@fg l=9018 top=100 b
@fg a=ブルー
[ブルー f=02]「Hey there, rookie.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Aaa...」[k]
Blue was standing in front of my house with Eric and a few guys.[k]
[ブルー f=02]「I heard you guys completed a quest.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Y-yes...」[k]
How did he hear that so quickly...?[k]
[ブルー f=02]「That's quite an accomplishment for someone who's just starting out. I'm impressed with your motivation.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「Y-yes, thank you.」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「Are you guys celebrating?」[k]
[マックス f=01]「Well, something like that.」[k]
[ブルー f=01]「If you want, why don't you let us celebrate with you? Your first quest!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What? You and your friends?」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「Sure, let's go.」[k]
@cl
[テオ f=12]「Oh...」[k]
[エリック f=01]「Come on, everyone, don't hesitate to come up!」[k]
Without my consent, Blue and Eric came into the room. Following them, the rest of the guys came in.[k]
[name n="Blue's Friend" f=thief_black_01]「Excuse me.」[k]
[name n="Blue's Friend" f=thief_red_01]「Wow, you live in a pretty nice room for a rookie!」[k]
[name n="Blue's Friend" f=bandit_blue_01]「Nice to meet you, [テオ].」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Oh, wait a minute...!」[k]
[textoff]
@out t=0
@w05
[texton]
Without giving me time to object, Blue's friends kept coming in one after another.[k]
They suddenly took over my room and started drinking without my permission.[k]
[textoff]
@out t=0
@w1
@bgf f=0008
[texton]
[name n="Blue's Friend" f=bandit_blue_01]「Okay, I'll have a drink too!」[k]
[name n="Blue's Friend" f=thief_red_01]「Ah, the drinks are so good.」[k]
[ブルー f=01]「Come on, guys, drink up. It's on me today.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Oh, um... Blue...」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「Hey, you, go get something to eat.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Eh?」[k]
[エリック f=05]「Didn't you hear Blue? Off you go.」[k]
