[テオ f=12]「Y-yes...」[k]
Sensing an atmosphere where I couldn't refuse, I decided to go and run the errand.[k]
[name n="Blue's Friend" f=thief_black_01]「Gahahahaha!」[k]
[name n="Blue's Friend" f=bandit_blue_01]「Hey! You haven't got the snacks yet?」[k]
