; 初めてのピンハネ
; 朝・自宅前
@bg f=0015
@mu f=town
[texton]
Next morning.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Good morning, Max.」[k]
[マックス f=13]「Hey, [テオ]. Yesterday was a disaster.」[k]
After that, Blue and his friends made themselves at home for a night of drinking that lasted well past midnight.[k]
The meal money that I paid for yesterday has not yet been returned to me.[k]
[マックス f=05]「Next time Blue and his friends come over, let's say no. If we accept them, there'll be no end to it.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Yeah, I will.」[k]
