[texton]
Blue expressed his anger with spine-chilling ferocity. Max apologized profusely to Blue.[k]
We had worked a full day and were deprived of more than 90% of our earnings. It was obvious that we were treated unreasonably, but in the face of Blue's anger, we couldn't say anything.[k]
He is a prominent veteran adventurer who is well known in the area. He is also a man of overwhelming ability. There was no way we, as newcomers, were going to go against Blue.[k]
