[ブルー f=02]「I was just looking for you guys.」[k]
@se f=paper
Then he takes out a sheet of paper from his pocket.[k]
To my surprise, Blue showed me a job sheet. The deadline was this evening.[k]
[ブルー f=02]「Rejoice! I have a job for you. Of course you'll take it, right?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Ehh...」[k]
[マックス f=13]「Thank you for going out of your way to help us... But we have other business to take care of today...」[k]
