[マックス f=11]「Waaaaah!」[k]
To our surprise, Blue smashed a nearby barrel with a single blow from his large sword![k]
[ブルー f=07]「I told you to do it without rattling on and on! I've just brought you a job, what's with that tone of voice?」[k]
[マックス f=12]「Eeeeek!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「S-sorry! We'll do that job right now!」[k]
