[texton w=1]
It was not an atmosphere that we could refuse. To appease Blue, who was in a rage, we accepted his request without hesitation and went to work.[k]
I turned down the job gently, but he got so angry... I was struck with an unfathomable fear as I witnessed Blue's violent nature.[k]
And since it was very unlikely that I could handle two requests in one day, I had to decline the quest I had accepted myself...[k]
