; 夕方・自宅
@bg f=0008
@mu f=anxiety
[texton]
@se f=door2
[テオ f=05]「I'm home...」[k]
After completing the work imposed on me by Blue, I dragged my tired body home.[k]
[name n="Blue's Friend" f=bandit_blue_01]「Gahahahahahaha!」[k]
[name n="Blue's Friend" f=thief_red_01]「Hahahaha, that's a masterpiece!」[k]
[エリック f=01]「What? Looks like you're back.」[k]
[マックス f=12]「Oh... What? Why are Blue's friends at your house...?」[k]
[name n="Blue's Friend" f=thief_black_01]「Oh! Thanks for your hard work! We got started first.」[k]
While I was fulfilling Blue's request, Blue had gone into my house without permission and started drinking with his friends.[k]
I thought I locked the door, so why...?[k]
[ブルー e=帯刀 f=05]「Hey, I hope you got that job right.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Y-yes...」[k]
@se f=coin
I gave Blue all the rewards. Unlike last time, this time it was up to me to report to the client and even receive the reward.[k]
[ブルー f=02]「...Okay, there's definitely enough for the reward. It's not like they're sneaking it out.」[k]
[ブルー f=01]「Here, here's your share.」[k]
@se f=coinsingle
Blue took two gold coins out of the bag and tossed them carelessly on the floor. Apparently, each of these coins was a reward for me and Max.[k]
[マックス f=12]「Is that all...?」[k]
[ブルー f=08]「What is it? You got a problem with me?」[k]
[マックス f=13]「No, no, this is enough for me! Thank you very much!」[k]
Today was the day we were going to do the job ourselves and receive full compensation, but things turned out the same as last time...[k]
[ブルー f=06]「And I'll tell you one more thing.」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「From tomorrow, I'll be giving you jobs. So, you two, don't take a job on your own. Understood?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
[textoff]
@out
[texton]
The next day, and the day after that, Max and I had to do the jobs Blue had taken on for a meager reward.[k]
With the strong desire not to displease Blue, we continued to do the unprofitable work without complaint.[k]
[textoff]
@wait time=1000

; 翌日の夕方・自宅
; 勇気を出して抗議
@bg f=0008
[texton]
@se f=door2
[テオ f=05]「I'm home...」[k]
When I returned home, once again I found Blue and his friends drinking in the house without permission.[k]
[エリック f=05]「You're finally home, oops!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
I'm pretty sure I locked the door this morning. Why is the door open?[k]
[エリック f=05]「You, why do you lock the door?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Eh...」[k]
[エリック f=05]「With my lock-picking skills, it's easy to open the door, but it's a hassle to pry it open every time. So don't lock it again, it's too much trouble.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
It was as if it was a matter of course to pry open the lock and get in.[k]
[ブルー f=05]「You're finally home. Here, hand over today's reward quickly.」[k]
@se f=coin
He took the reward bag from my hand as if it were a matter of course. Then, as usual, he took out a gold coin and put it in my hand.[k]
[ブルー f=05]「I'll need you to go shopping as soon as possible. We're about to run out of booze, so get to it.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
This situation is clearly not right.[k]
I finally decided to say what I wanted to say.[k]
[テオ f=12]「Um! Gentlemen! Listen to me!」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「Huh?」[k]
The room is quiet for a moment as my voice echoes through the room.[k]
[name n="Blue's Friend" f=bandit_blue_01]「What the hell?」[k]
[エリック f=05]「What's up, [テオ]?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Um... Can you please stop drinking here from today?」[k]
[エリック f=07]「Huh?!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「This is my room. To be honest, I am annoyed. I want to have a good night's rest and be ready for work the next day.」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「...」[k]
[name n="Blue's Friend" f=thief_red_02]「...Tch.」[k]
[エリック f=05]「...Hey, what are you talking about, [テオ]?」[k]
Everyone's expressions become stiff.[k]
But I have to be brave enough to say it...! If I back down here, these drinking parties will continue forever.[k]
[テオ f=12]「Also, Blue.」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「...What.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「I'd like to refrain from accepting jobs you pick for us in the future.」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「...Huh?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「We'd rather accept our own jobs and be paid in full... So...」[k]
