Blue suddenly grabbed me![k]
@se f=grasp
He grabbed me by the chest and lifted me up with one hand.[k]
[テオ f=18]「Ugh...! Blue...」[k]
@se f=grasp
[ブルー f=07]「You son of a bitch... Who do you think you're talking to like that?」[k]
[テオ f=18]「I'm sorry... but things can't go on like this...」[k]
