[エリック f=05]「That's a terrible thing to say. Blue took an interest in you, and even found you jobs.」[k]
[name n="Blue's Friend" f=thief_red_01]「Oh no, he made Blue angry.」[k]
@se f=grasp
[テオ f=18]「Ugh...!」[k]
Blue stared at me with a demonic expression while keeping a grip on me.[k]
But I can't back down here...! We can't continue this relationship...![k]
