[テオ f=12]「...?」[k]
The anger that had just appeared on Blue's face disappeared, and he is now looking at us with a completely calm expression.[k]
[テオ f=12]「Blue...?」[k]
I wonder what's going on...? Maybe he's considering my plea...?[k]
[ブルー f=06]「...」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「...I understand. If you're going to go that far, you can do whatever you want.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「What...?」[k]
