[テオ f=12]「...!」[k]
Then Blue grinned.[k]
When I saw the sharp light behind those eyes, I instinctively knew that I could not go against Blue.[k]
His eyes were filled with deadly intent. He was staring at us with a sharp and ruthless gaze, as if he were a predator stalking its prey.[k]
If I really offend this person, I don't know what he will do to me. My life may even be in danger.[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
@fgf c=ブルー f=00
[ブルー f=02]「Hey, what's wrong?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「I said do what you want. Why aren't you happier?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...I'm sorry.」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「Huh?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「I take back what I said earlier. I am truly sorry...」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「...」[k]
