[エリック f=05]「Don't ever say anything unnecessary again!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
I stopped defying them. Yes, I had no choice from the beginning.[k]
Blue is by far the strongest and most fearsome man. Never make him your enemy. If you confront him, ruin awaits you.[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
I got involved with the wrong person.[k]
