@out
@wait time=1000

; 数ヶ月後・こき使われる日々
@bg f=0012
[texton]
For the next several months, Blue and his team worked me and Max hard day after day.[k]
Blue accepts work and pushes it on to me and Max.[k]
All the rewards were taken by Blue in exchange for a handful of gold coins. This was to continue for many months.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Looking around the bar, I see that many groups of adventurers are talking about their adventures.[k]
They are all full of life, and seem to be having a lot of fun.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Suddenly, I think of myself.[k]
...Why are only myself and Max suffering this way?[k]
So far, we are the only ones who have been bullied by Blue. I haven't seen Blue get involved with any other adventurers.[k]
While many adventurers are free to do their own thing, for some reason we are the only ones being preyed upon by Blue's gang.[k]
...It just so happened that I caught their eye. That's all.[k]
But why us? Why of all people...![k]
There's a reason why Blue won't touch anyone but us. If there are too many prey, they will collude and rebel.[k]
And no matter how powerful an adventurer Blue is, if he too blatantly displays poor behavior, he will make enemies with many other adventurers. If that were to happen, he would not be able to make it in this town.[k]
So they stick to me and Max as prey and do not reach out any further.[k]
All the adventurers in this town know about our situation. But they all turn a blind eye.[k]
They don't want the attention that getting involved with the two of us would bring them.[k]
And of course, that's all been carefully arranged by Blue.[k]
Honestly... it's impressive cunning.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
I realized that I was stuck in a hellhole of isolation.[k]
To say it was bad luck would be an understatement, but my heart is filled with an unfulfilled feeling.[k]
Will this go on forever?! Is there no way out?![k]
...No, there is a way out.[k]
To fight and win against Blue.[k]
But of course I can't do that. With my current abilities, I can never beat Blue.[k]
As we have seen before, Blue's ability is the real thing.[k]
The weak cannot resist the strong. That is the world of adventurers. I thought I understood that in my head, but in truth I did not understand it at all.[k]
Yes, I was naive.[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
@wait time=1000

; マックスの提案
@bg f=0015
@mu f=trick
@fg c=マックス f=06
[texton]
Then one day, Max made a suggestion.[k]
[マックス f=06]「You know, I've been thinking.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What is it?」[k]
[マックス f=06]「We can't resist Blue because we're not strong enough.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「I know that.」[k]
[マックス f=05]「Blue is super strong, of course, but on top of that there are his cronies. There are more than ten of them and only two of us. There is no way we can compete.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...So?」[k]
[マックス f=05]「In other words, we should get more party members!」[k]
[マックス f=05]「We need more members, maybe five or six. That way, even if we can't compete with Blue and the others, they won't hound us as much as they do now.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@wait time=1000

; 酒場で勧誘
@bg f=0012
@mu f=anxiety
[texton]
So we started recruiting members at the bar the next day.[k]
I approached every adventurer who came in and out of the tavern. It must have been close to a hundred.[k]
But... Not a single person joined.[k]
It was only natural, come to think of it. Everyone knew that Blue and his group had their eyes on me and Max. No one wanted anything to do with them.[k]
And we are still an inexperienced and weak party. No one would take the risk to work with us.[k]
Once again, I and Max were reminded that we were on our own.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@wait time=1000

; ギルドの受付
@bg f=0013
[texton]
[受付]「We will not get involved in any issues between parties. Sorry, but the parties concerned must resolve the issue among themselves.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Okay...」[k]
I even asked the guild to intervene. However, they never took any steps to do so.[k]
Surprisingly, Blue's gang were not a problem for the guild.[k]
Despite all they do, they have never been involved in a single problem involving the guild. So the guild had no reason to intervene.[k]
I remember that one adventurer once spilled the beans about Blue.[k]
He heard they didn't want any trouble with civilians or guild officials in this town. He is very thorough about that.[k]
The reason for this, of course, is that they wouldn't want to be declined work.[k]
They can't make a living if they don't get paid. And for adventurers, the biggest sponsor is the client. Therefore, they would never do anything to offend the guild that acts as an intermediary to clients.[k]
Blue was not only strong, but also never sloppy when it mattered.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@wait time=1000

; マックス逃亡
@bg f=0007
[texton]
[エリック f=05]「Hey, [テオ]. I heard you guys have been trying to recruit adventurers from the guild lately.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Y-yes...」[k]
The story of the solicitation was quickly heard by Blue. There seemed to be nothing we could do in this town to escape his scrutiny.[k]
[ブルー f=05]「I won't allow you to do something like that without my permission. Don't ever do it again.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「So you guys, join my party.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「What...?」[k]
[エリック f=05]「It's kind of a hassle to go through the process when the parties are separate. Some clients complain that the executing party and the requesting party are different. You guys are like Blue's henchmen now anyway, right?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「What the hell? What's wrong?」[k]
If we join Blue's party, we will completely lose our freedom. I want to completely refuse.[k]
But [―――][k]
[ブルー f=08]「Hey, you're not going to turn me down, are you?」[k]
[エリック f=07]「You son of a bitch! Blue offered to let you into his party, so I won't forgive you if you refuse!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「I'm home...」[k]
[テオ f=10]「I-I'll do it. I'll join Blue's party...」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「...Hmph. You should have said so sooner.」[k]
[エリック f=05]「OK. Then submit your application to join our party to the guild by the end of the day.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
I can't refuse Blue's orders. I have no choice.[k]
[ブルー f=05]「By the way, where did Max go?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Eh?」[k]
[エリック f=05]「I haven't seen him since yesterday. Even when I go to his lodgings, he's not there.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「What the...!」[k]
No way... Did Max run away?[k]
[ブルー f=05]「Hey, you're not hiding him, are you?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「No, no, I just found out too...」[k]
[エリック f=08]「Hey... Where the fuck did he go?」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「Let's go find him, Eric. Hey, [テオ], you've got until the end of the evening to do this job!」[k]
Blue handed me the instructions for the new job and went away with Eric.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@wait time=1000
[texton]
To my surprise, Max was found less than half a day later.[k]
Blue's gang have been terrorizing many adventurers who operate in this town. They seemingly got information on Max's location in no time.[k]
[textoff]
@bgf f=0014
[texton]
[マックス f=13]「I'm sorry, I'm sorry! It was just a little impulse...」[k]
[エリック f=01]「Hey, what should we do about this guy?」[k]
[ブルー f=15]「...Punishment. If you do something selfish, you have to be punished.」[k]
[マックス f=12]「Aaaah! I'm sorry, I'm sorry, please forgive me!」[k]
[エリック f=07]「Hey, come here!」[k]
[マックス f=11]「Aaahhh! Help meee!」[k]
[textoff]
