[texton]
Max was assaulted by Blue and his friends.[k]
When Max returned, his face was swollen and his body was covered with fresh wounds.[k]
After that incident, Max and I stopped any rebellion or plotting secession against Blue.[k]
We could no longer escape from Blue's party. It was engraved in the marrow of our bones.[k]
[textoff]

@wait time=1000
[texton]
[if exp='f.readPastEpisode']
	Six months passed in that state, and it has now been a year since my current life began.[k]
	Max and I continued to endure our lives without any hope, and now we reach the present.[k]
[else]
	Then, advancing to the point just after I met Maria and Riselle at the abandoned house in the forest.[k]
	Max and I continued to endure our lives without finding any hope.[k]
	After that, most of the reward we received for recovering the pendant was taken by Blue.[k]
[endif]

[textoff]
@wait time=1000

; 現在に戻る
@bg f=0008
@mu f=shadow
[texton]
@se f=door2
[name n="Blue's Friend" f=bandit_blue_01]「Gahahahahahaha!」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「Oh, [テオ], you're back.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
As normal, Blue and his friends party in my house without permission.[k]
Every night, a party was held. I had no choice but to watch in silence.[k]
[エリック f=05]「Hey, [テオ], go buy some booze.」[k]
He handed me some gold coins which Max and I had originally earned. They were part of the reward we received for fighting the bandits and recovering the pendant.[k]
[エリック f=05]「I'm sure you understand, but make sure that's all you spend it on.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...I'm off.」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@wait time=1000

@bg f=0016
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「Please, give me some alcohol.」[k]
[name n=Shopkeeper]「...Okay...」[k]
The townspeople, who were friendly in the beginning, have recently become unfriendly.[k]
I'm now a member of Blue's party, after all.[k]
I never thought I would be avoided by people... I really want to get away from them, too.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Can we continue to live like this?[k]
But how do you get away from Blue? If I try to escape, I'd end up like Max did.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
My heart is deep in despair.[k]
Yes, there is absolutely no escape. It is extremely difficult to escape from Blue's eyes in this town.[k]
Besides, even if we were to escape from Blue and escape this town, what would we do after that?[k]
As long as Blue is here, once I leave this town, there is no going back.[k]
Bravetown is a town for adventurers. Leaving here means giving up the path of an adventurer.[k]
But didn't I come to this town with a dream?! Can I let my dream of becoming a great adventurer be crushed so easily?![k]
[テオ f=08]「...Damn!」[k]
I want to escape from Blue and the others. But I don't want to give up my dream of becoming an adventurer.[k]
I could only suffer through the pain, with no bright future in sight.[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
@w05

@bg f=0062
@mu f=sad
[texton]
[テオ f=06]「...It's been a year since then.」[k]
My life as an adventurer wasn't supposed to be like this.[k]
There was an ideal life that I had envisioned. But that's now a pipe dream. In reality, I just continue to follow Blue's orders day after day.[k]
But [―――][k]
Lately, I've come to think that's fine.[k]
Blue is a truly frightening person. If you go against him, you don't know what he will do to you. So it's better to obey quietly.[k]
As long as we remain obedient, we are safe. To do well as adventurers, we should make as few enemies as possible.[k]
Yes, this is the most rational choice.[k]
[textoff]

@se f=door2
@bgf f=0008
[texton]
∗slam∗[k]
@fg c=ブルー e=帯刀 f=52
[ブルー f=52]「Whew, that was delicious.」[k]
Blue's gang, who had been drinking and eating at the bar, came back to my house, smelling of alcohol.[k]
@cl
They open the door to the apartment, and without hesitation, they come in and start relaxing as if it was their own.[k]
...It happens all the time. I don't care. It's wise to be quiet here.[k]
[ブルー f=52]「Phew～. I drank a little too much today.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Blue went straight to sleep, snoring loudly.[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
@wait time=1000

; 翌朝
@bg f=0007
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「...Huh?」[k]
Next morning when I woke up, Blue was gone.[k]
He went out this early this morning? That's unusual...[k]
@se f=door2
∗slam∗[k]
@fg c=ブルー e=帯刀 f=05
[ブルー f=05]「[テオ], you there?」[k]
Blue returned along with Eric.[k]
[テオ f=05]「What's wrong, Blue?」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「Me and Eric are going exploring today. You follow us. And tell Max to come, too.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Y-yes, I understand!」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@wait time=1000

; 町中
@bg f=0015
@mu f=town
[texton]
[マックス e=現在の装備 f=10]「It's rare that Blue and the others do any heavy lifting. Usually they just make us do it.」[k]
Max spoke to me in a whisper so that Blue and the others couldn't hear.[k]
[テオ e=現在の装備 f=06]「Today we're going into the ruins on the northern outskirts of town. Maybe they thought it was too much for us to accomplish on our own.」[k]
[マックス f=12]「The ruins... Oh, no... Rumor has it that there are some really strong monsters out there～!」[k]
Max looked frightened.[k]
[テオ f=06]「We'll be fine with Blue and the others. I know they're like that, but they are strong.」[k]
[マックス f=09]「I hope so...」[k]
Today's quest is to uncover treasure said to lie in ruins on the outskirts of town.[k]
The client requested some old materials from that treasure, but any other gold and silver found is fine to keep.[k]
In other words, there was potential to make a lot of money by completing this quest. So Blue would want to make sure of success.[k]
However, Max is right, the monsters that appear could be strong. It may be better to be cautious.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@wait time=500

