...Maybe there's something ahead. We should probably be careful.[k]
[マックス f=13]「Oh, um... Blue?」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「What is it?」[k]
[マックス f=13]「I don't think we should go any further. I have a bad feeling about this.」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「Huh? What, you scared? Let's get moving!」[k]
Max is understandably hesitant.[k]
