We barely remained standing after its barrage of fiery breath.[k]
What a huge difference in power...![k]
Even Blue could do nothing but try to protect himself. We could only stand frozen in the face of the overwhelming power of the most fearsome monster.[k]
If we don't do something, we'll be wiped out...![k]
It was clear from its initial attack that this wasn't an opponent we stood a chance against.[k]
But running would result in being seared by hellfire from behind.[k]
We are stuck in a state of limbo. Is there any way out?![k]
[name n=Dragon]「Grrrrr...」[k]
The monster licks its tongue and stares at the four of us.[k]
It is following our movements with shining eyes, intent on not letting its prey escape.[k]
It's desperate for food, so won't let go easily.[k]
[ブルー f=08]「Shit... In that case...」[k]
