;◇イベント05・悪魔との出会い
*ruin_5

; 町外れの遺跡Ｂ３
; しばらくフロアを歩き回るとイベント発生

; 遺跡の地下通路
[マックス f=12]「Hey, what if there's no way out of here?! There's no way up anywhere!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Don't give up! I'm sure if we look hard enough we'll find one...!」[k]
But I was also on the verge of a breakdown.[k]
It's completely enclosed. There is no exit anywhere. If there is a way out, it would be through the hole we fell down earlier.[k]
Do I have to climb up there? But the ceiling is too high for me to reach. Even if I could climb up, there is that monster beyond...[k]
Is everything going to be all right? Are we really going to die here?[k]
[マックス f=10]「Oh～ if only we had a [emb exp='o.リターン.displayName'] scroll!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「That's too expensive for us to afford.」[k]
[emb exp='o.リターン.displayName'] is a spell that allows you to return outside in an instant, from the depths of any labyrinth.[k]
There is a [emb exp='o.リターン.displayName'] scroll with the same effect. In other words, with it, we could get out of this basement right now.[k]
I would like to carry one of these items for such occasions, but they're too expensive, so out of reach for us new adventurers.[k]
...There's no point in asking for something we don't have. Now we have to focus on finding a way out.[k]
[マックス f=17]「Oh～! I can't take it anymore! We're done for!」[k]
Max's voice is pitiful and he is teary-eyed.[k]
[テオ f=12]「Don't give up! There's got to be a way out...!」[k]
[textoff]
@fg c=シュバルツ e=暗闇 f=99
[texton w=1]
[？？？]「There's no such thing! Too bad!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「...?!」[k]
Suddenly, someone spoke to us.[k]
[マックス f=12]「Who's there?!」[k]
@fg c=シュバルツ e=通常 f=00
A middle-aged adventurer emerged from the darkness.[k]
[テオ f=05]「You are...?!」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「My name is Schwarz. I've been wandering around here for days now.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「How many days...?」[k]
Apparently, someone got here before us. How did he end up here?[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「I've explored thoroughly. The only exit is the hole leading up...」[k]
So, the hole where the dragon was. He also fell down it.[k]
[マックス f=09]「Oh, no.」[k]
When Mr. Schwarz told us the cruel truth, Max and I were filled with disappointment.[k]
Have we run out of options...?![k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「...」[k]
[シュバルツ f=20]「...Actually, it's not like there's no chance of returning home from here.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What?!」[k]
[マックス f=12]「Can you help us?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「There is a possibility. But in order to do that...」[k]
@st
@clf
[？？？ v=vm001 buf=13]「Hehe! Looks like there are more poor lost children now ♪」[k]
[テオ f=05]「...!」[k]
A voice suddenly echoed through the room.[k]
[マックス f=11]「Who's that?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=08]「Damn you... devil...!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Devil?」[k]
@mu f=murmur
@fg c=悪魔 e=暗闇 f=99
[悪魔 v=vm002 f=99]「Heheheh...」[k]
@fg c=悪魔 e=通常
Then a figure about the height of a child gradually emerged from the darkness.[k]
[テオ f=11]「...!」[k]
[マックス f=12]「This... This is a devil...?」[k]
She had bat-like wings on her back and large horns on her head.[k]
She possesses the typical demonic appearance traits that were described by my father.[k]
But at first glance, she looks like a young girl. Rather than a devil, it might be more appropriate to call her a little devil.[k]
But a demon is still a demon, even if it looks like a child. Their power cannot be compared to that of ordinary monsters.[k]
In general, demons are fearsome beings that are distinct from other monsters. When I was a child, my father often told me about how terrifying they were.[k]
...But this girl-like demon even seems rather cute. Is she really a terrifying demon?[k]
[シュバルツ f=12]「Be on your guard! Despite appearances, this is an incredibly fearsome opponent!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Huh...?」[k]
[マックス f=12]「She doesn't look that way at all...」[k]
[シュバルツ f=20]「...In fact, I fought this devil a few days ago.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=08]「But I was no match for her! It was as if she was playing with me!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What the...?」[k]
Mr. Schwarz looks like an experienced adventurer. And yet he's saying he couldn't stand up to her at all?![k]
[悪魔 v=vm003 f=03]「Yes, yes, I played a lot ♪」[k]
[悪魔 v=vm004 f=05]「That guy was really, really weak. Barely worth talking about. Like, try again in 100 years?」[k]
[悪魔 v=vm005 f=04]「Honestly, I could have just killed him straight away. But that wouldn't have been any fun, so I decided to play with him some more ♪」[k]
[シュバルツ f=17]「Damn you...! What a fool...」[k]
[悪魔 v=vm006 f=03]「So today I came here to play with him again and found I have two more toys! That's so fun ♪ Gahahahahaha!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
The devil speaks with carefree amusement. Mr. Schwarz's story is probably not a lie.[k]
There is no way we can fight such a powerful opponent. Will our adventure end here after all?![k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
One question arises here.[k]
Why would such a high-ranking demon be lurking in the depths of these abandoned ruins?[k]
It's hard to imagine it would just be to make fun of people who'd fallen here...[k]
[悪魔 v=vm007 f=04]「Oh yeah, before I kill you guys, I'll tell you something good.」[k]
[悪魔 v=vm008 f=01]「You guys came to this dungeon because you saw a request in a nearby town, right?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What...?」[k]
She means the quest we received in Bravetown! How could this devil know about that?[k]
[悪魔 v=vm009 f=04]「Actually... I'm the one who made that request ♪」[k]
[テオ f=12]「...!」[k]
[マックス f=12]「W-what did you say?! 」[k]
It was this demon who made the request...?![k]
Putting aside the question of how the guild could have accepted a demon's request, why on earth would she go all the way to a human town to do so?[k]
[シュバルツ f=07]「You! What exactly are you planning?!」[k]
[悪魔 v=vm010 f=01]「I don't really have a plan. I just thought it would be fun to have a black dragon attack a human town ♪」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Black dragon...?」[k]
Presumably that dragon that attacked us upstairs?[k]
[悪魔 v=vm011 f=01]「The black dragon had been sleeping in these ruins for a long time, so I woke him up!」[k]
[悪魔 v=vm012 f=05]「But Mr. Dragon was so hungry that he couldn't move at all, let alone get out of here.」[k]
[悪魔 v=vm013 f=04]「But then how could he attack a human town? So, I thought I'd give Mr. Dragon a nice meal! ♪」[k]
[テオ f=12]「No way!」[k]
[悪魔 v=vm014 f=04]「Yes! If I put out a request like that one, a lot of money grubbing adventurers would gather at these ruins, right?」[k]
[悪魔 v=vm015 f=03]「They came here one after another, not knowing it was a dragon's lair. And they all ended up in Mr. Dragon's belly! ♪」[k]
[マックス f=12]「Ahh! Then that pile of bones...!」[k]
[シュバルツ f=12]「Damn you... devil...!」[k]
[悪魔 v=vm016 f=02]「So, he's much healthier now. But still not strong enough to break through the walls of these ruins, so he needs a little extra food.」[k]
The devil then held up her hand.[k]
[悪魔 v=vm017 f=15]「I'm tired of teasing you guys, so I'll feed you to Mr Dragon.」[k]
