[テオ f=05]「This place is...」[k]
The scenery around me had changed drastically.[k]
A familiar view of the town. Not the dungeon from earlier.[k]
[マックス f=03]「Wow, seriously?! We're back outside!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「We're saved...」[k]
Thanks to Mr. Schwarz's magic, we were able to return safely.[k]
...I thought for a while that I was going to die, but an unexpected turn of events saved my life.[k]
[テオ f=01]「Thank you very much. You saved us.」[k]
[textoff]
@fg c=シュバルツ f=00
[texton w=1]
[シュバルツ f=02]「It is I who should thank you. Without your demon-hunting powers, I would have had no choice but to rot in that underground prison. Thank you so much.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「I'm glad to be of service.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「It is an amazing power. Normally, when one has the misfortune to encounter such a high-ranking demon, one would have to give up. But even in a desperate crisis like that, you can go on.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「In other words, you have truly great potential. If you continue adventuring, I'm sure you will eventually achieve remarkable results.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「Well, I'll be off now. I'll be in town for a while, so you can rely on me if you need anything.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Yes, thank you.」[k]
[textoff]
