;■プロローグ４・逃亡

;◇イベント01・町の探索後、酒場へ
*escape_1

; 酒場の受付
@saveon
@mu f=bar
@bgf f=0012
@w05
[texton w=1]
When we arrived at the bar, we found out that Max and I had been evicted from Blue's party.[k]
[マックス f=10]「Apparently, they think we're dead. They really are heartless, aren't they?」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
According to the receptionist at the tavern, Blue and his friends had recently accepted a new quest and left for their next adventure.[k]
Maybe they got impatient because they lost the reward they were counting on due to the failure of this quest.[k]
[マックス f=06]「What do you say? Do we join Blue and the others? Or do we wait until they come back?」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「...I think I'm going to stop being an adventurer.」[k]
[マックス f=11]「What?!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「I came to this town with a dream of becoming a great adventurer... 」[k]
[テオ f=06]「But in the end, I was just used by a senior adventurer like Blue. I don't know what I became an adventurer for!」[k]
[マックス f=05]「Well, maybe, but... 」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...I was never cut out for it. My mother expected me to be a full-fledged demon hunter, but I'll never be like Dad.」[k]
[マックス f=05]「[テオ]...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「When I get back, I'm going to pack my bags and leave this town today. What about you?」[k]
[マックス f=06]「I... I still want to continue to adventure with you!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Max...」[k]
[マックス f=05]「Hey, [テオ], why don't you reconsider? It may be tough now, but I'm sure we'll be great adventurers someday!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Well, that's... 」[k]
[textoff]
@fg c=シュバルツ e=通常 f=00
[texton w=1]
[シュバルツ f=01]「Hey, [テオ], is that you?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Oh, Mr. Schwarz... 」[k]
Mr. Schwarz, who we'd just parted company with, came to the bar.[k]
[マックス f=03]「Yo, old man, we meet again! Did you come here for a drink too?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「Well, yes. But it's good you're here, as I had something to tell you.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「You wanted to talk to us?」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05

@bg f=0012
[texton w=1]
[テオ f=05]「What is it?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「Mmm, actually... 」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「I am retiring as an adventurer.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Eh?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「I'm getting old, after all... So I was planning to do so after that last adventure.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「But that one almost turned out to be the end of me. It is all thanks to you, [テオ], that I was able to return safely and live the rest of my life.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Oh, no, that's giving me too much credit...」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「I'm really grateful. So I give you this.」[k]
Schwarz placed a medal on the table.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Is this...?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「This is a Leadership Medal.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「...!」[k]
A Leadership Medal denotes someone with special party leadership qualifications.[k]
Usually, we ordinary adventurers cannot recruit or discover party members through the guild.[k]
You can only recruit people by talking to them directly.[k]
But it is different when you have a Leadership Medal. You can look at the roster in any of the the guild's affiliated facilities and choose any member you want.[k]
In addition, bearers can take on quests that ordinary adventurers cannot. Indeed, many privileges are granted.[k]
However, the only way to obtain the medal is to have someone give it to you specially, or to be recognized by the king of this country for remarkable performance.[k]
The medal is also a sign of trust in its owner. They are not attainable by just anyone.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Why would you give me something so valuable...?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「It's like I said. I'm really grateful to you.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「Besides, I'm retiring as an adventurer now, so what good would it do me? I was looking for someone to inherit it.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=01]「With your powers, you are a valuable asset in the fight against those troublesome beings called demons. It is someone like you who should have this. Take it.」[k]
[textoff]
@getitem item=統率者のメダル
[texton w=1]
[シュバルツ f=02]「Now you are free to recruit members and organize parties!」[k]
[シュバルツ f=01]「...It is true that you are still a novice adventurer. However, I believe that you will become a full-fledged adventurer as you dive into dungeons and gain more experience. Good luck!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Wait a minute!」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「Hmm? What's wrong?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「I appreciate the sentiment, but I still can't accept this... 」[k]
[シュバルツ f=07]「Why? This medal will definitely come in handy. You should not be shy here.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「No, it's not that... Actually, I'm thinking of quitting the adventuring business.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=07]「What?! Why would you...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Actually...」[k]
I told Mr. Schwarz about Blue's gang.[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「...I see what's going on.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「You guys have caught the attention of a rotten bunch. Yes, there are people like that who give the profession a bad name.」[k]
[マックス f=09]「They're a horrible bunch!」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「If you stay in this town, it may occur again.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「...」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「...So then, why don't you both come with me to Sapphire City?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Eh?」[k]
@mu f=city
[シュバルツ f=02]「It is my hometown and the place I intend to spend the rest of my life. I'll introduce you to the guild in Sapphire City.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What...?! Does that mean... 」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「I'll write you a letter of introduction. I'm a well-known adventurer there, if I say so myself, so it's no problem.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「A letter of introduction to the Sapphire City Guild... 」[k]
I hear that the guild in Sapphire City won't let you in without an introduction from someone.[k]
It's the reason I remained in Bravetown, despite Blue's treatment.[k]
However, if I'm allowed into the Sapphire City guild, that will no longer be necessary. In other words...![k]
[マックス f=03]「No way! Then we can escape from Blue and his gang and continue as adventurers! Hey, [テオ], we can't pass up this opportunity!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「A-are you sure you want to do this, Mr. Schwarz?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「Of course. You saved my life, so this is nothing. Besides, it would be a shame for an adventurer of your caliber to quit. What do you think?」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「You still want to be an adventurer, don't you?」[k]
[マックス f=01]「Yes, we can still do it! Let's try once more!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
This is a once in a lifetime opportunity. If all goes well, the path to achieving my dream will open up once again.[k]
It's not too late to try again, despite how things went here.[k]
[テオ f=05]「...Let's go to Sapphire City! We are very grateful for your kindness, Mr. Schwarz.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=01]「I see! That's good!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Thank you so much. I can't thank you enough... 」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「Well, it's no big deal. All right, if that's the case, let's leave before dark. It would be bad if they found out, right?」[k]
[マックス f=03]「Yeah, we gotta go before Blue comes back. Come on, [テオ]! Get ready to go right away!」[k]
[textoff]
@out

;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
; 設定
[iscript]

o.ブレイブタウン・北門.visible = o.ブレイブタウン・北門.appeared = true;
o.マルティナの酒場.events = [2];
o.森の中の廃屋入口.events = [3];
o.町外れの遺跡入口.events = [1];
o.自宅.events = [2];
o.テオ.levelUpToTheLast();
o.マックス.levelUpToTheLast();
o.テオ.recovery();
o.マックス.recovery();
o.シュバルツ.recovery();
o.遺跡の財宝.complete();

[endscript]
;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

; 体験版から継続ならここで現在に戻る
@jump storage="main04.scn" target=*return_from_past_episode cond='! f.readPastEpisode'

@wait time=500
@eval exp='o.ブレイブタウン.bgm = "city"'
@eval exp='game.gameVisible = true'
@layopt layer=0 visible=false
[texton w=0]
[シュバルツ f=00]「We leave this town this evening. You must come to the [b]north gate of Bravetown[/b] by the hour.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=00]「While they are gone, prepare for your journey.」[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


;◇イベント02・出発
*escape_2

; 夕方・町の出口
@saveon
@fa
@out
@w05
@mu f=ending
@bg f=0017
[texton w=1]
That evening...[k]
After preparing for the trip in a great hurry, Max, Mr. Schwartz, and I prepared to stealthily leave.[k]
Fortunately, Blue's gang never found us.[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「You're both ready. Let's go!」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Yes!」[k]
[マックス f=01]「Yeah!」[k]
We left for Sapphire City, far north of here.[k]
It was finally time to say goodbye to Bravetown, where I had worried and struggled for about a year as I aspired to become an adventurer.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
I had despaired of my relationship with Blue and given up on my life as an adventurer after getting involved with him. However today, that ends. This time, I will walk the path of my ideal adventurer.[k]
[textoff]
@out

;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
; 設定
[iscript]

o.ブレイブタウン.bgm = "town";
game.guest.entry(o.シュバルツ);
f.fountainForOpeningEvent = true;
game.clock = game.timeOfADay * 5 \ 8;
game.gameFrame.updateClock();
game.view.close();
game.openDungeonView(%[map:"コリンズの森", x: 37, y: 1, way: "w"]);
o.コリンズの森.sky = "dawnforest";
game.view.skyLayer.loadImages("sky_" + o.コリンズの森.sky);
game.view.startExplore();

[endscript]
;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[eventoff]
